    "302006": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew... They were easier to deal with than Paimon had expected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What were you even expecting?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... super strong bandits? Or monsters taller than buildings dropping out of the sky? Or y'know, something like that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He looks super serious... We gotta stay on our A-game, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "...This is the one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aaaah!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Let's go in and take a look."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You carefully search the abandoned hospital..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Heeey! Alhaitham, we haven't found squat! Are you sure we aren't wasting our time here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Patience. Shani says she only hears the crying at night. We have time to burn."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Until then..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "I'm taking a break."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And just like that, he sits down... Wait, he even brought a book to read!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What are you reading? Let Paimon see!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Okay, sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... Umm... \"The 'natural position,' which is the positional propensity of an entity in 'natural motion,' in contrast with an object in 'forced motion'... Huh? When free from external influences, every entity... displays the tendency to follow its natural trajectory...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "So, you got that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon gives up! You keep reading your book... See ya!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How is he so relaxed? Look at him, reading an impossible book in a creepy place like this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You know, it wouldn't kill you to read a book once in a while, either."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Paimon's your Teyvat travel guide! Paimon knows plenty of useful stuff already!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And anyway, it's not Paimon's fault that the books people read in Sumeru are so complicated..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Okay, okay, Paimon's the best."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe it's time to spread your wings and become learned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, what good is that gonna do for you? You're acting like one of those annoying grown-ups who go around nagging people to focus on their studies!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The more you learn, the more money you can earn to support me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, what gives? Shouldn't you be the one providing for Paimon!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Isn't that what I'm doing now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, right... Okay then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um, thank you for working so hard and earning so much Mora... If it weren't for you, Paimon would probably still be floating around in the ocean somewhere... Hehe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Thank you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're welcome."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*yawn* Paimon's getting so sleepy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? What was that sound?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "There it is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "It's coming from that direction."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is the sound coming from here? Paimon's not seeing anything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "It's from below."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh?! But there's no way we can get down there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Something is off about the interior here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Hmm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "As I thought. There's a hidden structure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa... It's like they tucked another hospital into this one..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It looks like there are other mechanisms around here. Let's keep exploring!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
