    "302012": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Cyno",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "There's something here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "What's this...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "It's buried in the sand... Looks like we'll need to roll up our sleeves and do some work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And Paimon thought running around everywhere was already enough work!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Now isn't the time for complaining, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, okay... So we have to dig it out? Whatever's down there looks like it's buried really deep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "With some effort, you manage to retrieve the buried objects."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "These are likely fragments of an Akademiya-developed device, something akin to a headset."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Looks like there were more than one Village Keeper. They must have been escorted this way, because there are device fragments scattered around here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Let's split up and search the area. Chances are that we'll find other things nearby."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Everyone goes in different directions and starts digging in the sand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "After a short while, you dig up another device nearby."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is this what we're searching for? It looks kinda scary..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "This is definitely a device used to extract divine knowledge."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "How did it end up buried in the sand? That can't have been part of the plan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "They must've been attacked along the way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, what!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Isak",
                    "T": "Grandpa... I hope you're okay..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Don't worry, your grandpa's gonna be fine!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Razak didn't display any signs of starvation or dehydration, which means that they left fairly recently."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "We should be able to catch up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "One more thing: Given that the device had been entirely covered by sand..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "I believe the attack must have happened prior to the sandstorm."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I agree."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "Let's keep going. They can't have gone far."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
